Accept: application/json

### Predict a focus rating from temperature
POST {{base}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "currentTemperature": 22,
  "maxTemp": 24,
  "minTemp": 20,
  "meanTemp": 22
}

### Invalid prediction payload returns 422
POST {{base}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "currentTemperature": 22,
  "maxTemp": 19,
  "minTemp": 20,
  "meanTemp": 22
}
